lead_paragraph: Somerset swept aside Nottinghamshire to stay in the hunt for the English County Championship on Thursday, but Yorkshire and Middlesex could still clinch the title with a day's play remaining in their clash at Lord's.

headline.print_headline: Somerset Go Top as Rivals Set for Lord's Finale
